{"tid":2303241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜Doncic...（認真）","createTime":"2020-11-27T18:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T09:29:53.000Z","uid":247085,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd7b04376666adf1647ef96f9cac409a0a747cf","tid":2303241,"uid":247085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:25:52.000Z","msg":"細個開始睇波果陣好拎憎LA Clippers，覺得Beverley、Paul George、Morris好拎茅（當年Playoff Beverley一?批暈Westbrook），次次進攻都好似教科書一?既戰術好悶<br />\n<br />\n到佢地退晒休，先知果D老練既技術／走位係好野黎<br />\n<br />\nKyle Anderson既獨特節奏、Ingram（全盛時期）既First Step、Andrew Wiggins對贏波既執著，都係到退休／收左皮先發現佢地原來咁拎勁<br />\n<br />\n高登仔好多人都反Doncic，但係老實講佢既Foot Work技術、Clutch Shots能力、對比賽既執著，冇人比得上佢（我覺得依家Lamelo Ball&gt;&gt;Doncic）<br />\n<br />\n我諗Doncic最多都係打多1、2年就退休，其實睇得1場得1場，好好珍惜<br />\n<br />\n利申：Dlo年代湖迷"},{"pid":"19e9de84c245db0972b655a07bed966c756a2bdb","tid":2303241,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:30:58.000Z","msg":"我最撚驚打打下又有人中支那肺炎，<br />\n到時又停撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"abf40d12143226cd020c2ca00166f7872b03954d","tid":2303241,"uid":247085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"19e9de84c245db0972b655a07bed966c756a2bdb","tid":2303241,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:30:58.000Z","msg":"我最撚驚打打下又有人中支那肺炎，<br />\n到時又停撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母臭閪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:40:29.000Z","msg":"放心好大機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21dc4ee9bbdf35fa1960b2509bfeaadb1eab1f0f","tid":2303241,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T20:03:05.000Z","msg":"我諗Doncic最多都係打多1、2年就退休<br />\nwhy?"},{"pid":"131966313827856409c504ab836fd17b8e0ceb81","tid":2303241,"uid":229834,"lik